### Get ALL movies
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/movies_extended

### Get a SINGLE movie by ID
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/movies_extended/1

### 1. Add a new movie
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/movies_extended
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "year": "2010",
  "description": "A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology."
}

### 2. Update a movie
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/movies_extended/9
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Inception: Special Edition",
  "director": "Christopher Nolan",
  "year": "2010",
  "description": "A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology."
}

### 3. Try to update a non-existent movie
PUT http://127.0.0.1:8000/movies_extended/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Ghost Movie",
  "director": "Unknown",
  "year": "2020",
  "description": "This movie does not exist."
}

### 4. Delete a specific movie
DELETE http://127.0.0.1:8000/movies_extended/10

